{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2248/comments/17399438.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:35288afa1650..4706ce718031?path=gazebo%2Fcommon%2FCommonIface.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2248/_/diff#comment-17399438"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 2248, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/2248.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/2248"}}, "title": "Plot export"}, "content": {"raw": "We could use `boost::filesystem::exists` here and remove the `stat.h` dependency that I believe is not portable. Something like this (I haven't tested):\n\n\n```\n#!c++\n\n{\n  std::string result = _pathAndName + \".\" + _extension;\n  int count = 0;\n\n  // Check if file exists and change name accordingly\n  while (boost::filesystem::exists(result))\n  {\n    ++count;\n    result = _pathAndName + \"(\" + std::to_string(count) + \").\" + _extension;\n  }\n\n  return result;\n}\n```\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>We could use <code>boost::filesystem::exists</code> here and remove the <code>stat.h</code> dependency that I believe is not portable. Something like this (I haven't tested):</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">string</span> <span class=\"n\">result</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">_pathAndName</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;.&quot;</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">_extension</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"kt\">int</span> <span class=\"n\">count</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"c1\">// Check if file exists and change name accordingly</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">while</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">boost</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">filesystem</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">exists</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">result</span><span class=\"p\">))</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">++</span><span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">result</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">_pathAndName</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;(&quot;</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">std</span><span class=\"o\">::</span><span class=\"n\">to_string</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;).&quot;</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">_extension</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">result</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2016-04-18T16:54:37.643688+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Carlos Ag\u00fcero", "uuid": "{da8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/692bf15758111acaddae4da15a47f9e5d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsCA-0.png"}}, "nickname": "caguero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:4ded1ddf-947e-4154-bbd1-3dba24f1bdbd"}, "inline": {"to": 137, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "gazebo/common/CommonIface.cc"}, "updated_on": "2016-04-18T17:19:09.011141+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 17399438}